*Neko* je otišao u šetnju. (Someone went for a walk.)

*Nekog* sam danas sreo u gradu. (I met someone in the city today.)

Pitaj *njega* da li zna. (Ask him if he knows.)

*Nekim* slučajem došli smo na isto mesto. (By some chance we came to the same place.)

*Nekoj* je to uspelo. (Someone succeeded at that.)